  "title": "⚠️Petrol Station Cashier / Pump Attendant ⚠️",
  "description": "<h3><strong>🛑Salary &amp; Benefits🛑</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Cashier: $2,305/month</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Pump Attendant: $1,700–$1,800/month</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Uniform and training provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3>\n<p>We are hiring <strong>Cashiers and Pump Attendants</strong> for our petrol station. Candidates must be able to work on weekends and rotate shifts.</p>\n<h3><strong>💠Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Serve customers and handle payments (cash, NETS, credit card)</li>\n  <li>Assist with fueling and ensure safety procedures are followed</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness of the station and replenish stock</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>💠Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Physically fit, reliable, and customer-oriented</li>\n  <li>Able to work <strong>6 days a week, weekends, and rotating shifts</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9611</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
